# âœ¨ :sparkles: ---------- New feature (feat)
# ğŸ‰ :tada: -------------- Major feature release worth celebrating (feat)
# ğŸš€ :rocket: ------------ Performance improvements (feat)
# ğŸ¨ :art: --------------- Visual changes like CSS styling (feat)
# ğŸ’„ :lipstick: ---------- UI improvements (feat)
# ğŸ”’ï¸ :lock: -------------- Fix typos (docs)
# âœï¸ :pencil: ------------ Security improvements (feat)
# ğŸ“ :memo: -------------- Documentation updates (docs)
